reviewText: For years we only had DISNEY'S BRAND SPANKING NEW DOUG'S HALLOWEEN SPECIAL DOUG'S VAMPIRE CAPER and DOUG'S FIRST MOVIE on VHS. We also bought Nickelodian's DOUG on DVD from AMAZON a few years ago So I finally bought the entire DISNEY'S BRAND SPANKING NEW DOUG on VHS for my father's birthday. UNFORTUNATELY DISNEY'S DOUG isn't available on DVD so we only have 8 episodes on VHS We have the entire NICKELODIAN DOUG series though on DVD every episode ' DOUG SO MUCH IT'S PART OF MY CHILDHOOD
My oldest son loved getting this video for a gift. He watches it all the time. It was shipped as promised and it was as described in ad.

Teenage boys love Doug.  They find all of his antics hysterically funny, no matter what they are or what episode of his series they are in.  Any Doug volume is a good choice for a teen.  I recommend this one.
Teenagers love Doug.  They find him hysterically funny, no matter which episode they are reading.  This book was a big hit for a teen boy and I would recommend it.
